\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Benchmark suite metadata. AgentBench-OpenClaw (AB-OC): 40 tasks across 7 domains. PinchBench (PB): 23 real-world productivity tasks. Scoring: PinchBench uses a three-tier system (automated + LLM-judge + hybrid); AgentBench-OC uses a 4-layer composite (55\% objective, 45\% self-evaluated). ``Low-scoring tasks'' are those that score below 0.5 on the Base (Seed 1.8) condition; the memory domain on AgentBench-OC is a structural outlier scoring exactly 50.0 across all model variants.}}{8}{table.caption.5}\protected@file@percent }
